16. How do you process large CSV files w/o running to memory issue ?
- use spark dataframes (not pandas - this loads the whole file into memory on single machine & will often crash for large datasets)
- Explicitly define the schema
- read required cols
- filte early
- tune partitions (Aim for 100-250 MB per partition)
- Avoid collect & huge display()
- Persist wisely (if reused multiple times)
- Convert CSV -> delta / parquet 
- CLuster sizing matters

